---
import SectionLabel from "./SectionLabel.astro";
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 px-4">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto reveal">
    <SectionLabel label="About" />

    <div class="terminal-titlebar rounded-t">
      <span class="dot bg-red-500/80"></span>
      <span class="dot bg-yellow-500/80"></span>
      <span class="dot bg-green-500/80"></span>
      <span class="ml-2 text-fg/60">about.txt</span>
    </div>

    <div class="terminal-block rounded-b border-t-0 p-6 sm:p-8 space-y-6">
      <p class="font-body text-sm text-muted mb-2">
        <span class="text-accent">$</span> cat about.txt
      </p>

      <div class="font-body text-fg/85 text-sm leading-relaxed space-y-4">
        <p>
          CS & Data Science student at <span class="text-accent">UC Berkeley</span> with a <span class="text-accent">3.97 GPA</span>,
          building at the intersection of machine learning, data engineering, and full-stack development.
          I thrive on turning complex data into actionable systems — from GNNs predicting chip power
          to RAG-powered chess coaches.
        </p>
        <p>
          Currently pushing the boundaries of <span class="text-fg terminal-glow-sm">neurotech ML</span> at Berkeley,
          decoding EEG signals for gait prediction. Previously shipped production ML at Synopsys and
          led engineering teams shipping real products used by thousands.
        </p>
        <p>
          When I'm not in the terminal, I'm probably thinking about how to optimize something —
          or building something new that probably shouldn't exist but does anyway.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8">
        <p class="font-display text-xs text-accent mb-3">// system_stats:</p>
        <div class="font-body text-xs sm:text-sm border border-border-muted bg-bg/50 overflow-x-auto">
          <table class="w-full">
            <tbody>
              <tr class="border-b border-border-muted">
                <td class="px-3 py-2 text-muted whitespace-nowrap">┌─────────────────┐</td>
                <td class="px-3 py-2 text-muted whitespace-nowrap">┌────────────────────┐</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-border-muted">
                <td class="px-3 py-2 whitespace-nowrap"><span class="text-muted">│</span> <span class="text-fg/70">university</span></td>
                <td class="px-3 py-2 whitespace-nowrap"><span class="text-muted">│</span> <span class="text-accent">UC Berkeley</span></td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-border-muted">
                <td class="px-3 py-2 whitespace-nowrap"><span class="text-muted">│</span> <span class="text-fg/70">major</span></td>
                <td class="px-3 py-2 whitespace-nowrap"><span class="text-muted">│</span> <span class="text-accent">CS & Data Science</span></td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-border-muted">
                <td class="px-3 py-2 whitespace-nowrap"><span class="text-muted">│</span> <span class="text-fg/70">gpa</span></td>
                <td class="px-3 py-2 whitespace-nowrap"><span class="text-muted">│</span> <span class="text-accent">3.97 / 4.00</span></td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-border-muted">
                <td class="px-3 py-2 whitespace-nowrap"><span class="text-muted">│</span> <span class="text-fg/70">focus</span></td>
                <td class="px-3 py-2 whitespace-nowrap"><span class="text-muted">│</span> <span class="text-fg">ML · Data · Full-Stack</span></td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="px-3 py-2 text-muted whitespace-nowrap">└─────────────────┘</td>
                <td class="px-3 py-2 text-muted whitespace-nowrap">└────────────────────┘</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
